01:01:48,480 --> 01:01:54,000
And then you get data from the people who managed 
to find that thing about what they did with it.  

742
01:01:54,000 --> 01:01:59,120
But you don't get any data about what they didn't 
do with it. And you certainly don't get any data  

743
01:01:59,120 --> 01:02:03,280
about the people who never found it, who never 
tried it. Maybe they landed on your website and  

