mode of like, okay, great. Now let's go as fast  

748
01:02:28,080 --> 01:02:34,400
as possible and get that out into customer's 
hands. But if you don't take this step first,  

749
01:02:34,400 --> 01:02:39,760
it's actually kind of counterintuitive that going 
fast can actually slow you down in the long run.

